name: Morris Magneto G5 HD Big Twin '36-'69 - Auto Advance
description:
FREE SHIPPING
G-5  Fully Automatic Morris Magneto for '69 and earlier Big Twin Harley-Davidsons. Same features as theM5, and more... no interference problems with cylinders, frame, and relay boss. Also fits aftermarket Gen/Alt cases, in the conventional distributor hole. 

Comes with Black magneto cap.

All magnetos are made to order by Morris Magnetos. Please allow 7-10 days prep before your order ships.

name: Morris Magneto MM74E HD Big Twin '36-'69
description:
FREE SHIPPING
Morris Magneto's MM74Emagneto fits Harley-Davidson Big Twins 1936 through 1969. Knuckleheads, Panheads and Shovelheads. Built in advance and retard helps prevent kickbacks. Easy installation (does require grinding of the regulator boss on the cases on Knuckles and Shovels), no chopping head fins or smashing in pushrod covers. The drive separates from the magneto head and you can install the drive shaft without having to pull the front head. No-leak drive housing. Only from Morris Magneto! 
Retail Price : $939.00

Comes with Black magneto cap.

All magnetos are made to order by Morris Magnetos. Please allow 7-10 days prep before your order ships.

name: JOE HUNT MAGNETO '74 TYPE TWIN HD '36 -'69 #1274
description:
FREE SHIPPING
A beautiful, functional high performance part for your early 74 Harley. Rugged construction insures long dependable service. The Joe Hunt Harley 74 magneto is completely self contained requiring only a switch and primary wire. The stock electrical system may be retained for street use or removed completely for competition. This magneto features two piece construction for ease of application. 

This magneto includes a black cap. 

All magnetos are made to order by Hunt Magnetos. Please allow 7-10 days preparation before your order ships.

name: Wassell Style Tank
description:
Two Gallon Capacity.

The Wassell Style tank features heavy gauge steel construction (tank shells are stamped from 1mm (approx. 19 ga. steel) , 1/4" NPT petcock bungs and undrilled DIY mounting tabs for custom installation. It takes a British-style gas cap for unparalleled chopper authenticity.

Tanks are pressure tested at the factory, but it is highly recommended you or your painter pressure test it again before painting; it's cheap insurance!

name: Sporty Tank
description:
The mounts on this tank are stock fitment on 1996 - 2003 Harley-Davidson Sportsters.

These 2.5 gallon gas tanks are top quality, nice thick steel with a center mount American style filler bung that accepts stock style screw in filler cap, a 22mm stock H-D style petcock bung, and a vent tube that is soldered shut. To run the vent tube just melt the solder out, though the gas cap bung is set up for a vented cap anyway. Another quality part from Cleveland CycleWerks.

Take a look at the first two photos below for the dimensions on this tank.

Tanks are pressure tested at the factory, but it is highly recommended you or your painter pressure test it again before painting; it's cheap insurance!

name: No School Choppers-License Plate Bracket/Vertical/Left Side Mount
description:
This is the tail light bracket by No School Choppers and accepts both the 28 and 33 style tail lights. The holes to bolt the light assembly to are larger diameter allowing for slightly different brands of lights to fit, though the 28 and 33 tail lights we sell are a sure-fire fit.

- Left hand side mount (left side when sitting on bike).
- The mounting holes are 1 3/4" center to center. - 10 gauge laser cut steel construction w/ black powder coat finish.
- Axle mount plate is 3/16" steel with TIG welded fabrication. Stronger then any on the market.
- Chrome license plate frame and mounting hardware included.

These license plate brackets will fit either a 1" or a 3/4" axle. They are drilled for 1" and come with a stainless steel stepped spacer to allow it to be run on a 3/4" axle with no modifications.

name: Biltwell, Inc. Kung Fu 1" Natural Gum Rubber Grips
description:
From the mouth of Biltwell: "We believe motorcycle grips should be simple and comfortable. These BMX-inspired units are exactly that. Thick ends are durable, small flanges are attractive and a million little rubber fins are comfy."

One grip is 1" OD and the other 1-1/8" OD to slip over your throttle.

name: Biltwell, Inc. Sanderson Cast Black Stainless Foot Pegs
description: Finally classic styling for later model bikes! These bulletproof, investment cast stainless steel pegs are designed for bikes with with female mounts. They fit late model HD Sportsters and big twins and many other universal applications. The male mounting portion is 4130 Chromoly for unbeatable strength. Infinitely adjustable so you can rotate the peg body into any position, then lock it down. This feature comes in handy if you have forward controls, like to tilt your pegs back a little bit or otherwise adjust your ergonomics. Black ED, cast stainless steel! Sold per pair.

name: Biltwell, Inc. Tracker Handlebars 1" No Dimples Black
description:
Biltwell handlebars are precision crafted with 100% seamless 4130 chromoly. The wall thickness of our tubing is a burly .120". All handlebars are now available smooth for custom applications, or with dimples to accommodate original equipment throttle, brake and clutch assemblies. 

** This bar is knurled in the handlebar mounting area. The knurling is 1" wide and measure 4.5 inches across outside of knurling to outside of knurling.
